<div id="ftn166">
<p class="MsoFootnoteText"><a href="#_ftnref166" id="_ftn166" name="_ftn166" title=""><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><sub><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><sub>[166]</sub></span></sub></span></a> As of December 2018, PHC employed 1,690 contract workers and 3,007 day laborers in Lokutu, 1,692 contract workers and 2,794 day laborers in Yaligimba; and 859 contract workers and 640 day laborers in Boteka. Human Rights Watch interview with Fanny Salmon, Feronia Deputy Sustainability Director, Kinshasa, February 11, 2019.</p>
</div>

<div id="ftn167">
<p class="MsoFootnoteText"><a href="#_ftnref167" id="_ftn167" name="_ftn167" title=""><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><sub><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><sub>[167]</sub></span></sub></span></a> Human Rights Watch interview with a PHC former divisional manager, Mbandaka, November 22, 2018. 11 workers told Human Rights Watch this was an established practice.</p>
</div>

<div id="ftn168">
<p class="MsoFootnoteText"><a href="#_ftnref168" id="_ftn168" name="_ftn168" title=""><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><sub><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><sub>[168]</sub></span></sub></span></a> Human Rights Watch interview with Worker #23, Lokutu, January 25, 2019.</p>
</div>

<div id="ftn169">
<p class="MsoFootnoteText"><a href="#_ftnref169" id="_ftn169" name="_ftn169" title=""><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><sub><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><sub>[169]</sub></span></sub></span></a> Thirteen day laborers told Human Rights Watch that the company did not pay their wages in full.</p>
</div>

<div id="ftn170">
<p class="MsoFootnoteText"><a href="#_ftnref170" id="_ftn170" name="_ftn170" title=""><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><sub><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><sub>[170]</sub></span></sub></span></a> Human Rights Watch interviewed 13 workers across the three plantations who said their salaries had at times not being paid in full, some also said their colleagues –in particular day workers– had experienced the same.</p>
</div>

<div id="ftn171">
<p class="MsoFootnoteText"><a href="#_ftnref171" id="_ftn171" name="_ftn171" title=""><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><sub><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><sub>[171]</sub></span></sub></span></a> Human Rights Watch interview with Worker #62, Lokutu, January 27, 2019.</p>
