<div id="ftn256">
<p class="MsoFootnoteText"><a href="#_ftnref256" id="_ftn256" name="_ftn256" title=""><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><sub><span class="MsoFootnoteReference"><sub>[256]</sub></span></sub></span></a> BIO response to Human Rights Watch information request, February 6, 2019; copy on file. CDC Group’s Chief Executive Nick O’Donohue told Human Rights Watch CDC staff visited the plantations at least every six months; CDC Group’s response to Human Rights Watch information request, April 30, 2019, copy on file.</p>
